Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.51,0:00:11.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在俺還算年輕 也曾叛逆時
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.67,0:00:16.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最大的對手是個叫鳴人的小子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.19,0:00:18.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人 鳴人…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.23,0:00:21.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個危及我自由 且相當了不起的小子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.05,0:00:26.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時光長河不曾間斷 徑直向前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.31,0:00:30.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時的鳴人處於人生低谷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.66,0:00:33.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助離開了木葉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.13,0:00:35.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人覺得自己非常無能
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.43,0:00:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是在綱手成為第五代火影之後
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.90,0:00:41.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他和自來也踏上旅途之前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.34,0:00:47.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我安靜地聽著
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.20,0:00:50.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我與鳴人的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.06,0:00:55.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找寵物
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.20,0:00:58.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在還給我這種准新手任務啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.44,0:01:00.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拒絕
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.57,0:01:03.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有必須派遣你的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.16,0:01:10.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.67,0:01:17.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙又逃跑了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.37,0:01:19.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且在那之後
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.11,0:01:23.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說它接受過不亞於忍犬的忍鴕鳥訓練
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.66,0:01:26.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍鴕鳥…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.40,0:01:30.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果將此任務當作普通的尋找寵物可就大錯特錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.84,0:01:35.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…第五代
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.41,0:01:38.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又有什麼雜活要做嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.89,0:01:40.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任命你為隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.90,0:01:43.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長 當隊長嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.07,0:01:45.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我來當
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.46,0:01:46.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鋼子鐵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.74,0:01:50.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你即刻率領臨時小隊前去捕獲鴕鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.22,0:01:51.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.54,0:01:53.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴕鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.66,0:01:57.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴕鳥逃到了木葉演習場的附近
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.66,0:01:59.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,演習場
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.20,0:02:00.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道就是我們中忍考試時
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.00,0:02:03.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出現巨大蜈蚣什麼的地方嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.51,0:02:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中忍考試借用的是第44號演習場
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.40,0:02:10.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次要拜託你們前往第0號演習場
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.37,0:02:12.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有第0號演習場嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.82,0:02:18.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過第0號已經不再作為演習場使用了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.83,0:02:21.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不僅如此
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.43,0:02:25.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡還是聚集了世界各地飛禽走獸的保護區
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.47,0:02:28.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前已經禁止人類進入了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.33,0:02:31.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那還是我小時候的事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.79,0:02:35.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的生態圈如何我也毫無頭緒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.30,0:02:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別名禁獵區
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.32,0:02:45.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡就是第0號演習場了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.19,0:02:47.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 那個鴕鳥混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.23,0:02:49.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要跑來這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.84,0:02:52.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看那傢伙會逃到這裡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.86,0:02:55.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我手癢了 腳也控制不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.15,0:02:57.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是什麼樣的對手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.77,0:02:59.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都要將其打得服服帖帖
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.02,0:03:04.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說你們三人之前有合作過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.61,0:03:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一說的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.56,0:03:09.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.54,0:03:10.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.70,0:03:11.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要問為何的話 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.84,0:03:14.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 我明白了 進去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.82,0:03:20.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 第五代
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.24,0:03:24.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是隨便挑了幾個下忍扔給我的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.21,0:03:27.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,子鐵做隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.85,0:03:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 出雲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.90,0:03:31.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就讓那傢伙一個人出任務…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.26,0:03:36.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我並不是計較你們倆之間的能力差距
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.57,0:03:39.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是讓碰巧閒著的子鐵…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.93,0:03:42.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以出雲 你就別想太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.80,0:03:46.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼沒讓我和子鐵一起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.70,0:03:49.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真煩人 你們這些寂寞小生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.90,0:05:39.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來就以一列縱隊前進
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.04,0:05:41.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前鋒由鳴人擔當
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.65,0:05:42.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.66,0:05:43.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來是我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.20,0:05:45.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦前鋒有任何動靜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.62,0:05:47.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就能立刻支援
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.47,0:05:48.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面是志乃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.85,0:05:50.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左右兩邊的警戒切不可怠慢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.01,0:05:53.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後是李 注意後方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.31,0:05:54.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.82,0:05:57.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該讓我殿後
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.11,0:05:58.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.07,0:05:59.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要問為何的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.19,0:06:02.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背後長有雙眼的人才適合殿後啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.47,0:06:05.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我後面確實沒長眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.46,0:06:06.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志乃有嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.12,0:06:10.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我並不是指背後真要長眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.48,0:06:11.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.52,0:06:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以利用許多眼睛來觀察
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.15,0:06:17.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就不能不繞圈子說話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.07,0:06:18.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那個 就是那個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.35,0:06:22.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的蟲子可以替你監視
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.08,0:06:23.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別急著下結論
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.05,0:06:25.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要問為何的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.36,0:06:27.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果隊長不首肯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.29,0:06:28.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就無法改變位置…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.24,0:06:29.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殿後就拜託你了 志乃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.22,0:06:31.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連同副隊長一職
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.46,0:06:35.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個班的副隊長應該是我才對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.51,0:06:37.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認識鴕鳥的只有我一個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.89,0:06:40.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才讓你做前鋒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.19,0:06:42.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.47,0:06:45.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.96,0:06:48.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴕鳥在哪兒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.14,0:06:50.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.09,0:06:52.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第五代可是這麼說的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.40,0:06:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只不過知道那傢伙的長相
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.68,0:06:57.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏身之處可一無所知
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.29,0:07:07.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第五代 幹嗎不分配一個探知型忍者參加這個任務
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.47,0:07:09.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如日向或是犬塚…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.09,0:07:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都出任務去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.39,0:07:15.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第五代…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.63,0:07:17.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那該怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.17,0:07:19.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我來找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.73,0:07:20.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志乃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.23,0:07:28.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是油女一族啊 那就拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.90,0:07:38.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒找到那只鴕鳥嗎 志乃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.91,0:07:41.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡範圍太大了 不要著急
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.51,0:07:44.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 這裡真像熱帶原始森林啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.88,0:07:49.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋 不准笑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.26,0:07:52.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因為你 又讓我出這種任務
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.85,0:07:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光說可沒用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.69,0:07:58.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…你就繼續吸引它的注意力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.27,0:07:59.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為…為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.06,0:08:01.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我趁機將其包圍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.32,0:08:12.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了 志乃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.15,0:08:15.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是應該的 不用客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.03,0:08:19.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 這種事就交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.46,0:08:22.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的爸爸是凸肚臍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.90,0:08:25.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會發笑啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.91,0:08:27.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它發笑也是正常的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.89,0:08:29.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你被鄙視了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.64,0:08:31.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.11,0:08:33.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴕鳥的確有爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.96,0:08:37.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是凸肚臍就不可能了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.63,0:08:39.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 真麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.65,0:08:41.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我說清楚啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.48,0:08:42.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要問為何的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.63,0:08:44.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為鴕鳥是卵生動物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.77,0:08:45.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有肚臍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.26,0:08:49.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 竟然被小瞧了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.72,0:08:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.80,0:08:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志乃 還沒好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.00,0:08:54.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.20,0:08:55.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.65,0:08:57.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感應不到蟲子的反應
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.16,0:09:04.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說…那些是…食蟲植物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.76,0:09:06.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小風羅 小節子 小群…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.74,0:09:09.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小野花 小米盧娃 小野茂 小暮 小戶…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.95,0:09:11.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜點 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.12,0:09:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的蟲子被吃掉一半了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.57,0:09:17.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕不會讓你給逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.78,0:09:20.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了 志乃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.48,0:09:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經無法前行了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.84,0:09:23.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要問為何的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.08,0:09:26.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能會喪失更多的蟲子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.94,0:09:29.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就繞路跟上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.45,0:09:37.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋 給我等著
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.95,0:09:39.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白癡 白癡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.90,0:09:42.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好快 不愧是鴕鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.42,0:09:44.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.30,0:09:47.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有凱老師真傳的腳力…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.79,0:09:49.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就快去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.41,0:09:50.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.95,0:09:55.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,濃眉還是一如既往地快嘛 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.16,0:10:03.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目標確認
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.62,0:10:11.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.47,0:10:16.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.17,0:10:23.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是外國的體術 拳擊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.85,0:10:28.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴕鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.97,0:10:31.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,濃眉那傢伙怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.89,0:10:34.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴕鳥 來吧 鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.85,0:10:35.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.47,0:10:37.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛說話了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.01,0:10:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就猜肯定會有追兵前來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.33,0:10:47.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到會是你 這也算緣分吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.20,0:10:53.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過緣盡於此了 鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.09,0:10:57.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要打倒你 然後重拾真正的自由
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.41,0:11:00.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不過打倒了鳴人 少瞎嚷嚷 鴕鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.27,0:11:03.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身為隊長的我還健在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.62,0:11:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.25,0:11:08.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就從你開始吧 鴕鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.19,0:11:10.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少瞧不起人類了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.64,0:11:12.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴕鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.81,0:11:15.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴕殺
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.32,0:11:20.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴕鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.23,0:11:25.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴕鳥制空斬
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.78,0:11:28.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.12,0:11:29.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.60,0:11:37.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起了 這次我要動真格的了 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.94,0:11:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴕鳥 鴕鳥旋風擊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.96,0:11:46.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 子鐵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.57,0:11:49.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.09,0:11:53.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴕鳥升龍彈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.08,0:11:58.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟你配合真不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.64,0:12:01.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才難道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.97,0:12:06.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴕鳥…閃耀踢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.87,0:12:11.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們總有一天要當上上忍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.70,0:12:15.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是走馬燈嗎 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.91,0:12:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死前會看到的那個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.36,0:12:24.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會死在這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.30,0:12:27.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對手不過是只鴕鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.63,0:12:34.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別得意忘形了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.66,0:12:36.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次換我做你的對手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.42,0:12:37.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.03,0:12:39.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先撤退吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.98,0:12:45.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此 拳頭變化多 速度快
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.58,0:12:48.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 光靠拳頭可贏不了我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.35,0:12:52.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是能用腿還有投技和關節技的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.73,0:12:56.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的拳路已經被我看穿了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.70,0:12:58.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說到底你不過是只動物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.89,0:13:00.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.39,0:13:04.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尾巴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.35,0:13:16.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一 二 三 雖然尾巴突襲讓我大吃一驚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.63,0:13:18.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不過是個簡單的組合拳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.80,0:13:21.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一 二 三 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.07,0:13:22.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這裡 到此為止了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.07,0:13:27.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的攻擊 從哪兒打來的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.26,0:13:34.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暫時撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.70,0:13:41.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們太輕敵了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.08,0:13:45.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 因為是動物 所以大意了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.29,0:13:47.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經不能稱為動物了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.47,0:13:50.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它們擁有將我們引開並逐個擊破的智慧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.66,0:13:53.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且會說話 能耍花招
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.17,0:13:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來不是隨便就能應付的對手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.70,0:13:57.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我們的任務是捕捉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.95,0:13:59.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如果不行就另想辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.05,0:14:01.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長真有魄力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.59,0:14:03.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為部下倍感安心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.41,0:14:06.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總比被鴕鳥或是袋鼠幹掉強吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.51,0:14:17.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好 人類
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.86,0:14:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快從這裡滾出去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.09,0:14:23.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡已經是我們動物的王國了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.06,0:14:25.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果想馴服我們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.03,0:14:28.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們會用尖牙和利爪回擊的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.33,0:14:30.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒有牙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.83,0:14:34.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴 你們別想抓到我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.55,0:14:37.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的行動代號 是禿鷹大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.95,0:14:40.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是鴕鳥 自稱什麼禿鷹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.88,0:14:42.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要你管
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.30,0:14:45.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想剝奪我們自由的人 絕不能放任不管
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.41,0:14:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們會讓你們見識一下忍者動物四獸士的厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.12,0:14:52.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼四獸士啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.88,0:14:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你識數嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.75,0:14:55.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.10,0:14:57.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經上了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.05,0:15:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.23,0:15:13.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,食蟻獸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.59,0:15:16.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙 是食蟲動物嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.57,0:15:17.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的蟲子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.24,0:15:18.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上吧 濃眉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.98,0:15:23.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.93,0:15:26.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 不會像剛才那樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.90,0:15:34.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會讓你逃掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.82,0:15:36.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,影分身術
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.26,0:15:44.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分身術
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.86,0:15:50.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一隻鴕鳥還會分身術
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.77,0:15:53.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分身始終是分身 實體只有一個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.14,0:16:01.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴕鳥會用影分身…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.64,0:16:04.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我發現了 隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.62,0:16:07.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些都是真的鴕鳥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.61,0:16:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經準備好伏兵了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.75,0:16:17.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.36,0:16:30.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是認真的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.16,0:16:33.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木葉旋風
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.74,0:16:35.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.61,0:16:36.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四獸士嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.07,0:16:39.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,李
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.83,0:16:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然不是你死就是我亡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.95,0:16:46.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.86,0:16:51.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.83,0:16:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得手了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.67,0:16:58.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,替身術
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.27,0:17:00.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長 後面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.10,0:17:02.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.15,0:17:09.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 子鐵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.38,0:17:11.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.90,0:17:14.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的配合真是不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.27,0:17:18.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那個 果然是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.72,0:17:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們總有一天要當上上忍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.84,0:17:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.78,0:17:28.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走馬燈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.25,0:17:34.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來我真要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.27,0:17:35.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 出雲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.11,0:17:37.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你的約定…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.10,0:17:39.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躲開 子鐵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.37,0:17:42.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都幻聽了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.03,0:17:46.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別放棄 站起來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.64,0:17:50.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴕鳥流星爆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.67,0:17:59.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,增援嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.46,0:18:01.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出雲 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.19,0:18:02.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用那招吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.52,0:18:04.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.58,0:18:17.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴕鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.21,0:18:19.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水遁.水飴拿原
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.43,0:18:27.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得手了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.38,0:18:28.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.87,0:18:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.36,0:18:39.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.51,0:18:46.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.82,0:18:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.88,0:18:52.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這邊也是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.72,0:18:58.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這邊總算也結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.62,0:19:05.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出雲 幸虧你來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.27,0:19:06.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.34,0:19:09.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你沒來的話 我就…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.52,0:19:11.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有個問題
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.29,0:19:14.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我丟下第五代給我的雜活…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.43,0:19:17.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去之後 我幫你解決
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.03,0:19:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.40,0:19:24.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別想再逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.20,0:19:26.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得你應該能理解的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.76,0:19:27.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.81,0:19:29.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個膠水
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.39,0:19:31.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好粘
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.04,0:19:33.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別以為我會放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.35,0:19:44.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是我跟鳴人的因緣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.37,0:19:47.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一直在干擾我的自由
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.62,0:19:49.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禿鷹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.85,0:19:52.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又逃走了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.32,0:19:58.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次再繼續吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.74,0:19:59.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.53,0:20:00.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.93,0:20:05.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禿鷹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.39,0:20:11.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白癡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.17,0:21:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,專為小李研製的青春飲品
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.42,0:21:51.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而其中不可缺少的便是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.21,0:21:52.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七色花
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.45,0:21:55.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是只盛開在木葉國境的七色山上的靈草
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.67,0:21:58.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,散發著七色之光 據說能醫治百病
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.18,0:22:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但珍貴的東西總是很難入手的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.53,0:22:01.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.71,0:22:03.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就由我去採回吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.71,0:22:06.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 火影忍者疾風傳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.93,0:22:09.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 青春的中藥丸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.36,0:22:12.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽我把話說完啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.27,0:22:18.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是自來也大人留下的暗號嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.61,0:22:23.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說鹿丸和暗號班正在解讀之中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.88,0:22:29.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼綱手大人都不和我們商量一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.10,0:22:33.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是讓我們從事看門 整理資料這種小事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.90,0:22:35.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的粉絲該難過了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.28,0:22:40.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們曾經是鹿丸的考官啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.33,0:22:42.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪像現在平起平坐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.03,0:22:44.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那傢伙比我們等級高吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.05,0:22:49.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 既然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.97,0:22:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要比那傢伙更早解開暗號
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.37,0:22:55.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓他大吃一驚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.69,0:22:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出雲 子鐵
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.45,0:23:00.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有事想要拜託你們…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.97,0:23:06.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.01,0:23:10.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.06,0:23:11.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有很大的誤會啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.15,0:23:13.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 等等 不對
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.72,0:23:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綱手大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.02,0:22:39.81,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(480,367)}出雲、子鐵：「聽我們的命令」
